General.Name: Zignsec AB
General.Description: ZignSec AB (publ) provides Software as a Service platform with digital real time solutions for customers due diligence and identity verification worldwide. Its platform offers a range of digital verification methods, such as online identity verification, identity document authentication, identity data verification, electronic IDs, identity document verification, biometric check, PEP and sanction check for individuals, phone number validation, business register checks, corporate document authentication, and sanction checks for entities, as well as officer, director, and owner identification services. The company also offers know your customer (KYC) and know your business (KYB) solutions, as well as operates orchestration platform for KYC and KYB compliance measures. It serves iGaming, funds and pension, insurance, eHealth, and ecommerce companies, as well as education, and banking and financial institutions. ZignSec AB (publ) was incorporated in 2015 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
